Titolo: A.D.A.M. The Inside Story

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: A.D.A.M. The Inside Story is a 1995 educational interactive CD-ROM. It was one in a series of titles made in collaboration between Columbia/HCA Healthcare Corporation and A.D.A.M. Software, alongside titles such as A.D.A.M. Life's Greatest Mysteries and A.D.A.M. Nine Month Miracle.